name: #3 POSTCARD FROM VALPARAISO, CHILE (front)
description:
There it is, my friend Tom.
Along the road, I have a lot of partners, nobody like him.

We went to Valparaiso to work on the street and in a hostel, just in January. We ended up leaving the hostel because the owner was very strange and bossy. 
 
He played music on the street and I sold postcards on bars, everything was great.

After all, we were so tired because of a full-time adventure.
On the last day, we went to see this sunset to the Concon dunes.
